parameters.name: START TIME
parameters.description:
Spacecraft event time (UT) at which the particle counting begins.       
      Time is given in the format of `yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss.sss'.

parameters.name: STOP TIME
parameters.description:
Spacecraft event time (UT) at which the particle counting ends.         
      Time is given in the format of `yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss.sss'.

parameters.name: SECTOR
parameters.description: LECP stepping platform position (1-8). Unknown if 9.

parameters.name: SCAN_DIR
parameters.description:
LECP scan direction of the sector                                       
      (1 = for increasing; -1 = for decreasing.

parameters.name: PL01_RATE
parameters.description:
Counting rate measured in energy channel PL01                           
      (30-53 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: PL02_RATE
parameters.description: Counting rate measured in energy channel PL02 (53-85 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: PL03_RATE
parameters.description:
Counting rate measured in energy channel PL03                           
      (85-139 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: PL04_RATE
parameters.description: Counting rate measured in energy channel PL04 (139-200 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: PL05_RATE
parameters.description:
Counting rate measured in energy channel PL05                           
      (200-550 keV/nuc. protons and ions).
